         = \n | commands         = \n | battles          = \n | awards           = \n | military_blank1  = \n | military_data1   = \n | military_blank2  = \n | military_data2   = \n | military_blank3  = \n | military_data3   = \n | military_blank4  = \n | military_data4   = \n | military_blank5  = \n | military_data5   = \n}}\n\n'''Tasleem''' is an Indian politician and a member of the [[16th Legislative Assembly of Uttar Pradesh]] of India. He represents the [[Najibabad (Assembly constituency)|Najibabad]] constituency of [[Uttar Pradesh]] and is a member of the [[Bahujan Samaj Party]] political party.<ref name=\" Member Profile \">{{cite news|title= Member Profile|publisher=[[Uttar Pradesh Legislative Assembly]] website|accessdate=Aug 2015|url=http://uplegisassembly.gov.in/ENGLISH/pdfs/members_profile/17.pdf}}</ref><ref name=\" 2012 Election Results \">{{cite news|title= 2012 Election Results|publisher=[[Election Commission of India]] website|accessdate=Aug 2015|url= http://eci.nic.in/eci_main/StatisticalReports/AE2012/Stats_Report_UP2012.pdf}}</ref><ref name=\"All MLAs from Assembly Constituency\">{{cite news|title=All MLAs from Assembly Constituency|publisher=Elections.in|accessdate=Aug 2015|url=http://www.elections.in/uttar-pradesh/assembly-constituencies/najibabad.html}}</ref>\n\n==Early life and education==\nTasleem was born in [[Bijnor district]], [[Uttar Pradesh]]. He has received education till [[twelfth grade]]. Before being elected as [[Member of the Legislative Assembly (India)|MLA]], he used to work as a [[businessperson]].<ref name=\" Member Profile \"/>\n\n==Political career==\nTasleem has been a [[Member of the Legislative Assembly (India)|MLA]] for two term.<ref name=\" Member Profile\"/> He represents the [[Najibabad (Assembly constituency)|Najibabad]] constituency and is a member of the Samajvadi party.\n\n==Posts Held==\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! # !! From !! To !! Position !! Comments\n|-\n| 01 ||March 2012 ||March 2017 || Member, [